Students in the same class, Lois, I met her and was able to marry her one week after Gilead.

00:21:35.740 --> 00:21:42.740
Arriving has a newlywed couple in a missionary home with seven other people.

00:21:42.740 --> 00:21:46.740
It was quite daunting, but we didn't let that face us.

00:21:46.740 --> 00:21:49.740
We were on a honeymoon.

00:21:49.740 --> 00:21:52.740
Columbia was a paradise, spiritually.

00:21:52.740 --> 00:21:55.740
We loved it so much.

00:21:55.740 --> 00:22:00.369
This was the kind of life we wanted.

00:22:00.369 --> 00:22:04.369
Lois was a great teacher in the ministry.

00:22:04.369 --> 00:22:06.369
I always enjoyed working with her.

00:22:06.369 --> 00:22:11.740
She was actually a great support for me.

00:22:11.740 --> 00:22:14.740
Obviously, Columbia had its risks.

00:22:14.740 --> 00:22:20.740
I remember in the mornings, sometimes it got to the point where I would look at Lois

00:22:20.740 --> 00:22:22.740
and she would look at me and we'd just say,

00:22:22.740 --> 00:22:25.740
if I don't see you, see in the paradise, you know.

00:22:25.740 --> 00:22:31.559
Columbia became our home.

00:22:31.559 --> 00:22:37.559
We traveled the length and breadth of the country and our different assignments.

00:22:37.559 --> 00:22:45.559
We'd been over 20 years in Columbia when it became very evident that Lois's mom would need our care.

00:22:45.559 --> 00:22:52.339
This, of course, would mean leaving her assignment.

00:22:52.339 --> 00:22:56.339
It almost tore my heart apart to leave Columbia.

00:22:57.339 --> 00:23:06.869
I felt I was abandoning so many privileges and my treasured assignment.

00:23:06.869 --> 00:23:15.869
In the USA, we were working as a team and I could see Lois really organized

00:23:15.869 --> 00:23:19.869
making the best of the situation.

00:23:19.869 --> 00:23:27.869
Helping her mom was really the source in a way of her deep joy.

00:23:27.869 --> 00:23:32.869
Helping others was just a way of life to Lois.

00:23:32.869 --> 00:23:40.869
It doesn't matter what privilege you have, what responsibility,

00:23:40.869 --> 00:23:45.869
the true happiness is always found in giving.

